title: Leonardo DiCaprio Got His Steak Salted by 'Salt Bae'
text:
Tweet Leonardo DiCaprio Got His Steak Salted by 'Salt Bae' 
The internet recently fell in love with Chef Nusret Gokce , who has been dubbed “Salt Bae” for his unique salting technique, and Leonardo DiCaprio just got his steak salted by the man himself! 
“Salt Bae” shared a photo of him salting Leo ‘s steak during a visit to his restaurant in Dubai on Thursday (February 2). 
Leo is seen sitting at the table with a toothpick in his mouth while watching in awe as his steak gets salted by the pro. 
Check it out below and watch the video the original viral video after! Feb 2, 2017 at 5:27am PST
